Interface Navs

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BootstrapElement<Tag,Navs>, Card.Navs, Consumer<Object>, Container<Navs>, Markup, NamedItemsContainer, Producer

    public interface Navs
extends BootstrapElement<Tag,Navs>, NamedItemsContainer, Card.Navs, Container<Navs>
    Navs with content. toHtmlElement returns the nav element.

      • getContentDiv

        Tag getContentDiv()
        Navs outputs nav container and content div one after another which works fine for horizontal tabs/pills. However, for vertial pills it outputs the pills above the content. Use this method and toHTMLElement() to output navs and content divs independently, e.g. each into a col in a row.
        Returns:
